name: TimeData Corporation
tag_list: ss7, qos, voip, phantom-traffic, calea, netflow
overview: TimeData’s SONAR is a managed solution for Service Providers (e.g., small telephone companies and mobile service operators), which: 1) Collects data from the switch, SS7, IP network and other sources upon installation at the Service Provider. 2) Identifies and categorizes revenue loss due to wireless reciprocal compensation, phantom traffic, VoIP, IPTV, and route arbitraging. 3) Provides performance metrics and 24x7 customizable alarms, and identifies extended area service, trunk group, switch, SS7, IP, QoS and network issues. 4) Provides CALEA compliance for Broadband.

funding_rounds.source_description: May 2009 TimeData completed its first close of the Series A round
